<button bindtap="onChangeKeyBoard1" type="primary">弹出默认键盘</button>
<button bindtap="onChangeKeyBoard2" type="primary">弹出带右侧栏的键盘</button>
<button bindtap="onChangeKeyBoard3" type="primary">弹出身份证号键盘</button>
<button bindtap="onChangeKeyBoard4" type="primary">弹出带标题的键盘</button>
<button bindtap="onChangeKeyBoard5" type="primary">弹出配置多个按键的键盘</button>
